<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Internship + Skill Gap Analyzer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="logo">✦ Student Portal</div>
      <div class="nav-pill">
        <a href="/" class="active">HOME</a>
        <a href="/student/internships">EXPLORE INTERNSHIPS</a>
        <a href="/external-jobs">LIVE JOBS</a>
        <a href="/student/register">REGISTER</a>
        <a href="/student/login">LOGIN</a>
        <a href="/student/dashboard">DASHBOARD</a>
        <a href="/company/register">COMPANY REGISTER</a>
        <a href="/company/login">COMPANY LOGIN</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="home-hero">
      <div class="home-hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Internship + Skill Gap Analyzer</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Track practical experience, manage certificates, build internship readiness,
          and create your student profile for future success.
        </p>
        <div class="home-actions">
          <a href="/student/register" class="btn-primary-glow">Student Register</a>
          <a href="/student/login" class="btn-light-pill">Student Login</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="module-gateway glass-card">
      <div class="module-copy">
        <span class="module-kicker">Integrated Main Modules</span>
        <h2>Choose a member module</h2>
        <p>Both modules share the same Prisma schema, one local database, and one Express app.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="module-bars">
        <a class="module-bar" href="/member3">
          <span>Member 3</span>
          <strong>SKILL PROGRESS TRACKER</strong>
          <small>Open 4 features: tracker, analytics, location filter, certificate generator</small>
        </a>
        <a class="module-bar" href="/member4">
          <span>Member 4</span>
          <strong>SKILL ANALYZER</strong>
          <small>Open 4 features: skill gap, matching, suggestions, chatbot</small>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      A simple student journey from registration to profile building and internship readiness.
    </p>

    <div class="how-grid">
      <div class="glass-card step-card">
        <h3>1. Create Account</h3>
        <p>Students register through a form and upload their resume for profile building.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card step-card">
        <h3>2. Complete Profile</h3>
        <p>Add academic background, skills, preferences, and experience details.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card step-card">
        <h3>3. Track Growth</h3>
        <p>Use the dashboards to prepare for internships and improve missing skills.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
